	<article id="post-2198" class="post-2198 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-civil-liberties category-current-affairs category-drugs-2 category-intelligence category-law category-leap category-mi5 category-mi6 category-politics category-prohibition-2 category-spies category-surveillance category-terrorism category-tours category-tv category-war-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-intelligence-2 tag-law-2 tag-leap tag-mi5 tag-mi6 tag-prohibition tag-spies-2 tag-terrorism-2 tag-war tag-war-on-drugs tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/silfur-egils-interview-iceland.html" title="Permalink to Silfur Egils Interview, Iceland" rel="bookmark">Silfur Egils Interview, Iceland</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/silfur-egils-interview-iceland.html" title="10:23" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-02-22T10:23:12+00:00" pubdate>February 22, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/02/silfur-egils-interview-iceland.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My recent inter­view on Iceland’s premier news dis­cus­sion show, <a href="http://www.ruv.is/sarpurinn/flokkar/silfur-egils">Sil­fur Egils</a>, hos­ted by the excel­lent Egill Helgason.</p>
<p>The name refers to an old Norse saga about a hero, an earlier Egill, throw­ing hand­fuls of sil­ver to the ground so he could make the Vik­ing politicos of the day scrabble around in the dirt try­ing to pick up the coins.</p>
<p><em>Plus ça change, plus c’est la même chose</em>.</p>
<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/dJ0oVrF27Og" height="315" width="560" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
